text: Biden announced free dental coverage for all seniors through Medicare
Biden announces Medicare stimulus that provides free dental work to all Seniors who need it! Crowns and implants included.
Joe Biden approved a new card that gives free health insurance to Americans who are 25 and older.
An image shared on Facebook claims President Joe Biden approved a healthcare card that would give $0 health, vision & dental benefits to those 25 and older.
President Joe Biden signed an executive order making health insurance free for qualifying Americans.
